#: templates/wpce-doc.php:2
msgid ""
"WP Cookies Enabler will not block cookies out of the box. Even though the "
"banner is displayed, you still have to put your hands on the code to "
"actually stop cookies. Here it is what you have to do."
msgstr ""
"WP Cookies Enabler non blocca automaticamente i cookie. Nonostante il banner "
"venga visualizzato, sarà necessario sporcarsi le mani con il codice per "
